  <metadata>
    <name>Rocky Canyon: Three Bears (FD20A) cues</name>
    <desc>FD20A. Freestone Creek | Official 6.72 mi; On-foot 13.1 mi; Door-to-door p75 4h 15m; Segments left 7 / 7. Check current Ridge to Rivers signage and conditions before leaving.</desc>
